<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product Restocked</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #10B981;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background-color: #10B981;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .stock-box {
            background-color: #ECFDF5;
            border-left: 4px solid #10B981;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>âœ¨ Back in Stock!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

        <p>Good news! A product on your wishlist is back in stock:</p>

        <h2 style="text-align: center;">{{productName}}</h2>

        <div class="stock-box">
            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #10B981;">Available Now!</p>
            {{#if quantity}}
            <p>Only {{quantity}} in stock</p>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if price}}
            <p style="font-size: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">${{price}}</p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <center>
            <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="button">Get It Now</a>
        </center>

        <p style="text-align: center; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;">Hurry - popular items sell fast!</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>You're receiving this email because you've enabled restock notifications.</p>
            <p><a href="{{actionUrl}}" style="color: #10B981;">Manage your notification preferences</a></p>
            <p>&copy; {{year}} TCG Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
